172
00:11:58,870 --> 00:12:00,570
Ini kekanak-kanakan.

173
00:12:00,570 --> 00:12:02,980
Aku sangat malu. Aku mau bersembunyi di suatu tempat.

174
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:06,779
Tapi... Jika mau melepaskanku,

175
00:12:06,779 --> 00:12:09,580
