- Aku...
- Tunggu, jangan katakan apa pun.

190
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:54,860
Aku

191
00:12:56,299 --> 00:12:57,600
menyukaimu.

192
00:13:01,029 --> 00:13:02,769
Bolehkah aku hanya mendengarkan yang ingin aku dengar?

193
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,779
Aku

194
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,610
menyukai

195
00:13:14,149 --> 00:13:15,250
kamu.

196
00:13:17,379 --> 00:13:18,779
Aku hanya mau mendengar...

197
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:22,090
Aku menyukaimu.

198
00:13:22,289 --> 00:13:23,820
Aku bersungguh-sungguh.

199
00:13:25,820 --> 00:13:27,230
Aku menyukaimu.

200
00:13:28,190 --> 00:13:30,629
Ucapan terakhirmu yang paling penting.

201
00:13:34,899 --> 00:13:36,399
Jadi, jangan menyukaiku.

202
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,769
Kamu mau aku bagaimana?

203
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:41,940
Jadi, aku akan berhenti di sini.

204
00:13:42,409 --> 00:13:43,710
Aku menyukaimu

205
00:13:44,539 --> 00:13:45,740
seperti aku menyukai Kak Chil Seong.

206
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:49,950
Kamu sangat jahat.

207
00:13:49,950 --> 00:13:52,220
Kamu sok baik.

208
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:53,750
Bisa-bisanya kamu begitu percaya diri?

209
00:13:53,889 --> 00:13:55,750
Kamu pengecut. Kamu pikir kamu jujur?

210
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:58,389
Tidak. Itu kejam dan menyakiti harga diriku.

211
00:13:58,389 --> 00:14:00,330
Aku sangat kesal dan kecewa.

212
00:14:00,330 --> 00:14:01,860
Kenapa kamu menjadikanku bahan tertawaan?

213
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:03,529
Haruskah aku berhenti?

214
00:14:06,330 --> 00:14:07,330
Pergilah.

215
00:14:08,399 --> 00:14:09,399
Pergi.

216
00:14:13,370 --> 00:14:14,509
Jangan pergi.

217
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:21,750
Jangan pergi...

218
00:14:29,759 --> 00:14:31,860
"Rumah Sakit Taeyang"

219
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,460
Kamu sudah sehat.

220
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:19,539
Hei, hentikan mobilnya.

221
00:15:22,909 --> 00:15:23,980
Tidak usah.

222
00:15:24,879 --> 00:15:26,110
Kamu kejam sekali.

223
00:15:26,350 --> 00:15:29,720
Dia sudah dekat ke restoran. Dia bisa berjalan.

224
00:15:30,179 --> 00:15:31,750
Hei, cepat menepi.

225
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:34,750
Kami sedang canggung, jadi, aku akan diam saja.

226
00:15:34,990 --> 00:15:37,590
Ajak dia ke restoran bersama kita.

227
00:15:37,590 --> 00:15:39,490
Cepat berhenti. Ayolah.

228
00:15:39,690 --> 00:15:41,730
Astaga.

229
00:15:50,299 --> 00:15:53,870
Selamat pagi, Pak Du. Kamu sudah dipulangkan?

