237
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,769
Cepatlah.

238
00:16:26,639 --> 00:16:28,669
Baiklah, kalau begitu.

239
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:44,090
Bagaimana soal makanan?

240
00:16:45,159 --> 00:16:47,090
